items.title: Webcomponents the Right Way
items.content_text:

items.title: Awesome Machine Learning
items.content_text:
### Python / Spiking Neural Networks

*   [Sinabs (⭐99)](https://github.com/synsense/sinabs) - A deep learning library for spiking neural networks which is based on PyTorch, focuses on fast training and supports inference on neuromorphic hardware.
*   [Tonic (⭐248)](https://github.com/neuromorphs/tonic) - A library that makes downloading publicly available neuromorphic datasets a breeze and provides event-based data transformation/augmentation pipelines.
items.content_html:
Python / Spiking Neural Networks

  • Sinabs (⭐99) - A deep learning library for spiking neural networks which is based on PyTorch, focuses on fast training and supports inference on neuromorphic hardware.
  • Tonic (⭐248) - A library that makes downloading publicly available neuromorphic datasets a breeze and provides event-based data transformation/augmentation pipelines.

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Completions / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [symfony (Akollade) (⭐4)](https://github.com/Akollade/symfony.plugin.zsh) - Adds completions for [Symfony](https://symfony.com/), including the `bin/console` and `sf` commands.
*   [yarn-extra-completion (⭐37)](https://github.com/BuonOmo/yarn-extra-completion) - Inspired by [lukechilds/zsh-better-npm-completion (⭐485)](https://github.com/lukechilds/zsh-better-npm-completion).
items.content_html:
